large  phylogenetic trees. Original features include:
(i) a colour-mediated overview  of magnified subtrees;
(ii) copy/cut/paste of (sub)trees within or between  windows;
(iii) compressing/ uncompressing subtrees; and (iv) managing sequence
files together with tree files.

